  "text": "Moreover, as shown in [CITATION_1] Theorem 1.3, the following converse is also true. Let Z be a complex manifold of complex dimension 2n + 1 satisfying the conditions (i), (ii) and (iii) Z is a holomorphic contact manifold with τ -invariant contact distribution transversal to real twistor lines, then Z is locally a twistor spaces of a pseudo quaternion-Kähler manifold.",
